Title: The Fountain Test
Author: Test Writer
Draft date: 2026-04-26

INT. LIVING ROOM - DAY

A small living room. Morning light through the curtains.

ALICE
Good morning.

BOB
(sarcastically)
Is it.

Alice sits down on the sofa.

ALICE
I think so.

BOB
Wonderful.

CUT TO:

EXT. GARDEN - DAY

The garden. Afternoon. Birds singing.

ALICE
Much better out here.

BOB
If you say so.

Charlie enters carrying an umbrella.

CHARLIE
It's going to rain.

ALICE
It always rains.

CHARLIE
That's the spirit.
